ZH: 我决定去旅游。
EN: I decided to go on a trip.

ZH: 他们决定明天开会。
EN: They decided to hold a meeting tomorrow.

ZH: 她决定辞职并寻找新的工作。
EN: She decided to quit her job and look for a new one.

ZH: 我们决定将会议推迟到下周。
EN: We decided to postpone the meeting until next week.

ZH: 他决定放弃这个项目。
EN: He decided to give up on this project.

ZH: 她决定告诉他实话。
EN: She decided to tell him the truth.

ZH: 他们决定搬到一个更大的房子里。
EN: They decided to move to a larger house.

ZH: 我决定学习一种新的外语。
EN: I decided to learn a new foreign language.

ZH: 他决定买一辆新车。
EN: He decided to buy a new car.

ZH: 她决定接受这个工作机会。
EN: She decided to take this job opportunity.

ZH: 我们决定参加那个音乐会。
EN: We decided to attend that concert.

ZH: 他们决定投资于股市。
EN: They decided to invest in the stock market.

ZH: 她决定进行进修学习。
EN: She decided to pursue further education.

ZH: 我决定吃素食。
EN: I decided to become a vegetarian.

ZH: 他们决定提前结婚。
EN: They decided to get married earlier.

ZH: 她决定参加演讲比赛。
EN: She decided to take part in the speech competition.

ZH: 我们决定组织一场慈善活动。
EN: We decided to organize a charity event.

ZH: 他决定请一段长假。
EN: He decided to take a long vacation.

ZH: 她决定继续追求自己的梦想。
EN: She decided to continue pursuing her dreams.

ZH: 我们决定向政府提出这个问题。
EN: We decided to raise this issue to the government.
